    "LIME is then utilized to explain the classification model's results by identifying the most important words highlighted by the model.",
    "These keywords are subsequently extracted and used as the basis for summarization, as they are considered the most central words in each paragraph.",
    "Kryściński et al. (2020) make the important observation that ensuring each summary sentence is entailed by a source sentence helps establish the factual accuracy of the summary, and they train a surrogate model to perform the entailment.",
